### ISS-001 — <!-- Incorrect error status on DB failure -->

**Severity**: <!-- high -->

**Category**: <!-- impl (code bug) -->

**Scenario**: <!-- SC-101 (Database unavailability) -->

**Description**: <!-- The API service returns HTTP 500 with a stack trace when PostgreSQL is unavailable, instead of HTTP 503 with a structured error response. -->

**Root Cause**: <!-- Missing try/catch in the database connection handler. The raw driver exception propagates to the HTTP layer unhandled. -->

**Resolution**: <!-- Added error handler in src/api/db.ts:42 that catches ConnectionError and returns 503 with {"error": "service_unavailable", "detail": "database connection failed"}. -->

**Status**: <!-- fixed — re-verified in SC-101 second run, now returns 503 as expected. -->

**Upstream Refs**: <!-- IMPL-CODE-001 (src/api/db.ts) -->

